text: The Al-Enezi family are an influential family in Kuwaiti politics and [Saudi politics]. There are four of the fifty elected parliamentarians in the Kuwaiti National Assembly that belong to the Enezi family: ex. Khalaf Al-Enezi. The Royal Family in some areas of the Middle East are related to the same family in Saudi Arabia and Bahrain and Kuwait. ==Surname== * Bandar Al-Enezi, Saudi footballer * Fahad Al Enezi, Kuwaiti footballer ==References== Category:Arabic-language surnames Category:Arab groups Category:Kuwaiti families Category:Tribes of Arabia
title: Al-Enezi
